  <verse number="24" style="v" />Therefore I say to you: Everything you pray and ask for, believe that you received it, and it will be yours.

  <verse number="25" style="v" />When you stand and pray, you must forgive whatever you have against anyone, so that your Father who is in heaven will also forgive you your transgressions."

  <verse number="26" style="v" />

<note caller="+" style="f">

  <char style="ft">The best ancient copies omit this verse  (see Mt. 6:15). Mk. 11:26 </char>

